# AGENTS.override.md - python_cli

## Profile

python_cli

## Purpose

Override base AGENTS.md guidance for a Python CLI project using src/, tests/, pytest, and CLI smoke checks.

## Read Order

1. AGENTS.md
2. AGENTS.override.md
3. PRODUCT.md
4. MVP.md
5. PROJECT_BOUNDARY.md
6. DATA_SCOPE.md
7. APPROVALS.md
8. PHASE_PLAN.md
9. STATUS.md
10. ACCEPTANCE_TRACE.md
11. SOURCE_INDEX.md
